    "description": "你将扮演一名巫师，在充满敌人的地牢中杀出一条生路。施放法术、躲避攻击，并收集战利品来升级你的角色。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037940/extras/c98853bf8fcff66454d4650705d806f5.poster.avif?t=1741708840\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037940/extras/c98853bf8fcff66454d4650705d806f5.webm?t=1741708840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037940/extras/c98853bf8fcff66454d4650705d806f5.mp4?t=1741708840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >慎重选择</h2>每局游戏都会提供许多选择来考验你的策略思维。你应该专注于哪种元素的法术？如何才能在最后一层生存下来？你愿意冒多大的风险？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037940/extras/479dfa46762362203c761917635e0106.poster.avif?t=1741708840\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037940/extras/479dfa46762362203c761917635e0106.webm?t=1741708840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037940/extras/479dfa46762362203c761917635e0106.mp4?t=1741708840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样性与重玩价值</h2>《Chaos Caster》经过精心设计，旨在将重玩价值最大化。每一种机制都会增加玩法多样性，确保每次游戏体验都独一无二。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037940/extras/8becd6e17f5781fb1bc86530f9b1a4a6.poster.avif?t=1741708840\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037940/extras/8becd6e17f5781fb1bc86530f9b1a4a6.webm?t=1741708840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037940/extras/8becd6e17f5781fb1bc86530f9b1a4a6.mp4?t=1741708840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
